From the "Absence registrations" page, enter a new absence:

<img width="" src="https://docs-test.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000821-0/ABSENCE1.png"><br>

<img width="" src="https://docs-test.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000821-0/ABSENCE2.png"><br>

<img width="" src="https://docs-test.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000821-0/ABSENCE3.png"><br>

The holiday type absence requires approval from the manager. 

The manager receives the approval request in Role Center. The approval request appears in Project manager role.

<img width="" src="https://docs-test.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000821-0/ABSENCE4.png"><br>

The manager can approve, reject or delegate the request. (the delegation must be set up in the associated approval workflow):

<img width="" src="https://docs-test.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000821-0/ABSENCE5.png"><br>

Once the absence is approved, the request line is linked to the time sheet line of the holiday day:

<img width="" src="https://docs-test.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000821-0/ABSENCE6.png"><br>

In time sheet:

<img width="" src="https://docs-test.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000821-0/ABSENCE7.png"><br>

